Encode:

got a nice stereo mic from cadance, no laughing, coughing,munching or any kind of sidenoise, very nice and clear voices
for the video i dont know who the source is from, got unknown cam, mrg, a russian,french and spanish, which all looked the same to me
the russian came out last had higher bitrate and less pixelation the perspective was already fixed too, so i went with that video as source.
so thx to all involved
fixed contrast brightness relation along with colouring, blurred the pixelation away and gained some sharpness back again.
pixelation is gone now video is nice
notice there were some subs missing for foreign parts took them from the halo cam which had them in the cam
and hardcoded them into my video.

its as good as it gets and def enjoyable like this
audio as mentioned very nice, lipsynced to my video
will do me till web-dl
enjoy
